 India 
In India multiple language are taught in primary schools continue to high school level as a part of curriculum. Selection of language based on the mother tongue of the area and choice. Apart from regional language like Sanskrit, the language taught is English. English speak spoken in India is known as Indian English at worldwide level because of pronunciation difference. 

